<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>lw nsyt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lw nsyt ḥby lyk ạftkr ạ̉ʿmạly byk
 ạftkr kl ạkẖtbạr jzt fyh lyl ạ̉w nhạr
 ạftkr rmz ạlʿạr ạftkr ạ̹ny fạdyk
 2- lw nsyt ḥḍny lyk ạftkr rʿạyty lyk
 lmạ tht fy ạlṭryq ṣrt lyk nʿm ạlrfyq
 ạftkr ạ̉y ṣdyq kạn bjnbk byrạʿyk
 3- lw nsyt ṣwty lyk ạftkr ḥmạyty lyk
 lmạ kẖḍt fy ạltjạrb lmạ jh ạ̹blys yḥạrb
 ywm mạ qlt wạ̹nt gẖạlb yạ ạ̹lhy slṭạny fyk</lyrics>
<author>kạml bqṭr, bytr jmạl</author>
